---
<section id="beranda" class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-16 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
    <img 
        src="/images/banner1.jpeg" 
        alt="Latar Belakang Taekwondo" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-center relative z-10">
    <div 
      class="text-2xl text-blue-200 mb-4 korean-title tracking-wider"
      data-aos="fade-down"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
    >
      Brigade
    </div>
    <h1 
      class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 korean-title"
      data-aos="fade-down"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
    >
      Taekwondo Club
    </h1>
    <p 
      class="text-xl text-gray-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
      data-aos-delay="200"
    >
      Membentuk juara dalam kehidupan melalui disiplin, rasa hormat, dan pengembangan diri.
    </p>
    <div 
      class="flex gap-4 justify-center"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
      data-aos-delay="400"
    >
      <a 
        href="#prinsip" 
        class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg inline-flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <span>Mulai Sekarang</span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a 
        href="#contact" 
        class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg border border-white/30"
      >
        Hubungi Kami
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full">
    <svg class="w-full h-16 text-white" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
      <path d="M0 100 C 20 0 50 0 100 100 Z" fill="currentColor"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  video {
    filter: brightness(0.8);
  }
</style>